(199, 1, '2017-03-10 12:59:13', '2017-03-10 12:59:13', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<p class=\"justify\">In carrying out its work, HRL Foundation relies on an extensive network of volunteers. Translation, legal research, awareness raising, drafting and proofreading – volunteers’ contributions and commitment provide the organization with valuable support.</p>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">If you would like to join us and have proven skills in the above-mentioned areas, please do not hesitate to get in touch. We will be happy to explain the various ways in which you can collaborate with us.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_text_separator title=\"Trail Watch\" color=\"custom\" accent_color=\"#ae9a67\" el_class=\"volunteer-heading\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Do you have a legal background and wish to take part in the Trial Watch project? Get in touch to join our team of volunteer researchers and translators!</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][contact-form-7 id=\"355\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_text_separator title=\"Translations\" color=\"custom\" accent_color=\"#ae9a67\" el_class=\"volunteer-heading\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Are you fluent in English and French? Get in touch to join our team of volunteer translators! Prior legal knowledge is preferable but not compulsory.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][contact-form-7 id=\"358\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Volunteer', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'volunteer', '', '', '2017-03-21 16:17:18', '2017-03-21 16:17:18', '', 0, 'http://localhost/hrlfoundation/?page_id=199', 0, 'page', '', 0),
