(207, 1, '2017-03-15 10:21:37', '2017-03-15 10:21:37', '[vc_row top_margin=\"1\" bottom_margin=\"1\"][vc_column][rev_slider_vc alias=\"lifeline 2\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row content_placement=\"middle\" el_class=\"first-background\"][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=\"Why a Human Rights Litigation Foundation?\" font_container=\"tag:h1|font_size:30|text_align:center|color:%23000000\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Istok%20Web%3Aregular%2Citalic%2C700%2C700italic|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p class=\"justify\">Every day, vulnerable people worldwide – including in European countries – are victims of gross Human Rights violations committed by States that, <em>too often</em>, remain unpunished. The access to justice for these victims is hindered due to multiple barriers: lack of financial means, lack of expertise, tolerance of national jurisdictions, political pressures … which make, in practice, this fundamental right illusory.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row heading_style=\"sec-heading\" col_title=\"<strong>Our</strong> Causes\"][vc_column][sh_our_causes number=\"6\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row parallax=\"true\" parallax_clr=\"blackish\" pattren=\"1\" top_margin=\"1\" parallax_bg=\"8\"][vc_column][sh_ceo_message number=\"3\" sorting_order=\"ASC\" category=\"38\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row col_title=\"<strong>Recent</strong> News\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\" heading_style=\"sec-heading\" col_title=\"<strong>Recent</strong> News\"][sh_recent_news number=\"6\" category=\"News\" margins=\"top\" title=\"Recent News\" heading_style=\"simple\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" heading_style=\"sec-heading\" col_title=\"<strong>Our Welfare</strong> Projects\"][sh_welfare_projects number=\"6\" category=\"all\" sort_by=\"0\" sorting_order=\"DESC\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '95-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-03-15 10:21:37', '2017-03-15 10:21:37', '', 95, 'http://localhost/