itigation at national level by way of working with and supporting NGOs with similar objectives as the HRL Foundation;</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"objective\"]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Promote access to justice for victims of gross human rights violations without the financial means to go to Court;</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row heading_style=\"sec-heading\" col_title=\"<strong>Our</strong> Causes\"][vc_column][sh_our_causes number=\"6\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row parallax=\"true\" parallax_clr=\"blackish\" pattren=\"1\" top_margin=\"1\" parallax_bg=\"8\"][vc_column][sh_ceo_message number=\"3\" sorting_order=\"ASC\" category=\"38\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row col_title=\"<strong>Recent</strong> News\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\" heading_style=\"sec-heading\" col_title=\"<strong>Recent</strong> News\"][sh_recent_news number=\"6\" category=\"News\" margins=\"top\" title=\"Recent News\" heading_style=\"simple\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" heading_style=\"sec-heading\" col_title=\"<strong>Our Welfare</strong> Projects\"][sh_welfare_projects number=\"6\" category=\"all\" sort_by=\"0\" sorting_order=\"DESC\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '95-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-03-15 11:08:39', '2017-03-15 11:08:39', '', 95, 'http://localhost/hrlfoundation/2017/03/15/95-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
