(272, 1, '2017-03-21 14:53:58', '2017-03-21 14:53:58', '<p class=\"justify\">Axelle is a third year student in European Law at Maastricht University. Next year, she will be doing a Master in Globalisation and Human Rights at the same University. Her strong interest in human rights developed from the fact that not a day goes by without she -like everybody else- hears about various fundamental rights violations taking place throughout the world. Her home country -Belgium- is also concerned. She does not value success at the cost of others and this constitutes one of the reasons why she only sees herself work in the field of human rights later on. She wants to see those situations of violation redressed, and deeply believes in the potential of the Human Rights Litigation Foundation to effectively contribute to this objective.</p>', 'Axelle Delcuve', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '81-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-03-21 14:53:58', '2017-03-21 14:53:58', '', 81, 'http://localhost/hrlfoundation/2017/03/18/81-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
