(280, 1, '2017-03-18 08:09:02', '2017-03-18 08:09:02', '<p class=\"justify\">Berfin Altinisik is a Law student at the Vrije Universiteit Brussel (VUB), Belgium. Currently, she is enrolled in her first year of the Master International and European Law. Already at an early age, Berfin was passionate about the never ending battle for justice, being confronted with discrimination as the daughter of political refugees. Her interest in human rights and human rights protection originates from this desire for justice and the belief that every individual is entitled to equal rights. Litigation is a key element in the judicial enforcement of human rights. Berfin strongly believes the Human Rights Litigation Foundation can improve the human rights protection, not only in Europe, but in every corner of the world.</p>', 'Berfin Altinisik', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'berfin-altinisik', '', '', '2017-04-01 10:42:28', '2017-04-01 10:42:28', '', 0, 'http://localhost/hrlfoundation/?post_type=dict_team&#038;p=280', 0, 'dict_team', '', 0),
