(341, 1, '2017-04-06 11:23:25', '2017-04-06 11:23:25', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_text_separator title=\"Video Explainer\" color=\"custom\" accent_color=\"#ae9a67\" el_class=\"vision-header\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]<iframe style=\"text-align: center;\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Jr8HKurQlvU?rel=0\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\n<p class=\"justify\">The HRL Foundation organises several fundraising activities to promote external support for its programmes. It will, among others, look for external supporters in Foundations, businesses, lotteries and individual supporters.</p>\n<p class=\"justify\">Publicity and transparency are key elements in the code of conduct of the HRL Foundation. We will regularly publish reports, update the website and other (electronic) channels about our activities and funding. We will share our successes by publishing what programmes and activities were funded by which supporter and what was achieved with that support: our success is your success.</p>\n<p class=\"justify\">With your support we can help most vulnerable groups of people by facilitating access to justice. All donations will be used for the establishment of the HRL Foundation and for its first program: The UN Program. Supporters of this project will receive infinite gratitude and publicity through our website, reports, and other (electronic) platforms.</p>\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"support-banner\"][vc_column][sh_donation_parallax_full_page title=\"Donate now!\" desc=\"Bank transfer:\nHuman Rights Litigation Foundation\nBE84 3630 3329 2359\nBIC: BBRUBEBB\" btn_txt=\"DONATE\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Support Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '195-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-04-06 11:23:25', '2017-04-06 11:23:25', '', 195, 'http://localhost/hrlfoundation/2017/03/20/195-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
