(412, 1, '2017-03-21 14:49:59', '2017-03-21 14:49:59', '<p class=\"justify\">Jessica has been a lawyer at the Brussels Bar since 2015. She holds a Master’s degree in Public Law from the Université Libre de Bruxelles (U.L.B.) as well as a Master’s degree in Human Rights from the Université Saint-Louis. Before joining the Bar, Jessica completed a six months internship at the United Nations High Commissioner for Refugees (UNHCR), Europe Bureau, in Brussels. She also voluntary gave courses on the asylum procedure to unaccompanied minors in the Fedasil first reception centre in Neder-over-Hembeek. Since early 2017, Jessica is practising within Just Rights law firm, in collaboration with Adv. Chihaoui.</p>', 'Jessica Davila-Ardittis', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '3-jessica-davila-ardittis', '', '', '2017-07-13 18:59:48', '2017-07-13 18:59:48', '', 0, 'http://localhost/hrlfoundation/?post_type=dict_team&#038;p=412', 0, 'dict_team', '', 0),
