(415, 1, '2017-03-21 14:51:58', '2017-03-21 14:51:58', '<p class=\"justify\">Laura holds a Master’s Degree in Law from the Catholic University of Louvain where she specialized in EU law and human rights law. Afterwards, she completed a three months internship at the Wallonia-Brussels Delegation in Geneva, followed by a six months internship at the Legal Policy Office of the Office of the UN High Commissioner for Human Rights (OHCHR) where she gained practical experience in human rights law in general and in the UN human rights system in particular.</p>', 'Laura Trigaux', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '5-laura-trigaux', '', '', '2017-07-26 09:39:26', '2017-07-26 09:39:26', '', 0, 'http://localhost/hrlfoundation/?post_type=dict_team&#038;p=415', 0, 'dict_team', '', 0),
