(438, 1, '2017-03-22 14:19:37', '2017-03-22 14:19:37', '[vc_row top_margin=\"1\" bottom_margin=\"1\"][vc_column][rev_slider_vc alias=\"lifeline 2\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row content_placement=\"middle\" el_class=\"first-background\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Why a Human Rights Litigation Foundation?\" font_container=\"tag:h1|font_size:20|text_align:center|color:%23000000\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Istok%20Web%3Aregular%2Citalic%2C700%2C700italic|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal\"][vc_empty_space height=\"20px\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p class=\"justify\">Every day, vulnerable people worldwide – including in European countries – are victims of gross Human Rights violations committed by States that, <em>too often</em>, remain unpunished. The access to justice for these victims is hindered due to multiple barriers: lack of financial means, lack of expertise, tolerance of national jurisdictions, political pressures … which make, in practice, this fundamental right illusory.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\r\n<p class=\"justify\">Furthermore, these Human Rights violations are often due to structural problems within the State, which cause a high number of victims as well as potential ones. However, the Human Rights litigation is currently mainly individual and no real strategic action is taken in order to tackle the source of the problem.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\r\n<p class=\"justify\">From this assessment was born the idea to create this Human Rights Litigation Foundation (HRL Foundation), which actions will be guided by these two main objectives:</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style=\"font-size: 17px; font-family: Istok Web; font-weight: bold; color: #ae9a67; padding-bottom: 10px; text-align: left;\">1) Promote a real and effective access to justice for the most vulnerable people -</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">whether due to their personal status or the particular situation they are facing – that are victims of gross Human Rights violations committed by States, by overcoming the existing barriers;</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style=\"font-size: 17px; font-family: Istok Web; font-weight: bold; color: #ae9a67; padding-bottom: 10px; text-align: left;\">2) Promote Human Rights through Strategic Litigation,</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">which will allow to address the Human Rights violations caused by structural deficiencies and have an impact not just on one but on all the individuals placed in a similar situation.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_column_text]\r\n<p class=\"justify\">The HRL Foundation have designed several programmes, all aimed at achieving these two objectives, although each through a different approach.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row parallax=\"true\" parallax_bg=\"431\"][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=\"Specific Objectives\" font_container=\"tag:h2|font_size:30|text_align:center|color:%23ae9a67\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Istok%20Web%3Aregular%2Citalic%2C700%2C700italic|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal\"][vc_empty_space][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"objective\"]\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li class=\"objective\">Raise funds through donations, sponsoring, and crowdfunding for the promotion of human rights litigation at national and international level;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"10px\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"objective\"]\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li class=\"objective\">Promote human rights litigation at national level by way of working with and supporting NGOs with similar objectives as the HRL Foundation;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"10px\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"objective\"]\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li class=\"objective\">Promote collaboration between Human Rights actors across Europe;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"30px\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"objective\"]\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li class=\"objective\">Promote access to justice for vulnerable groups of people, such as ethnic minorities, children, immigrants including asylum seekers, LGBTs, people with disabilities, detainees, the mentally or physically ill, and more;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"objective\"]\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li class=\"objective\">Promote litigation before institutions such as the European Court of Human Rights, and promote compliance with the judgment of these Courts;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"10px\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"objective\"]\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li class=\"objective\">Promote access to justice for victims of gross human rights violations without the financial means to go to Court;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"objective\"]\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li class=\"objective\">Protect and support human rights activists and defenders around the world;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"25px\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"objective\"]\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li class=\"objective\">Promote education and training of human rights activists and defenders around the world;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row col_title=\"<strong>Recent</strong> News\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\" heading_style=\"sec-heading\" col_title=\"<strong>Recent</strong> News\"][sh_recent_news number=\"6\" category=\"News\" margins=\"top\" title=\"Recent News\" heading_style=\"simple\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" heading_style=\"sec-heading\" col_title=\"<strong>Our</strong> Projects\"][sh_welfare_projects number=\"6\" category=\"project\" sort_by=\"0\" sorting_order=\"DESC\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row parallax=\"true\" pattren=\"1\" top_margin=\"1\" parallax_bg=\"227\"][vc_column][sh_ceo_message number=\"6\" overlap=\"true\" cat=\"testimonials\" sort_by=\"0\" sorting_order=\"ASC\" category=\"38\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '95-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-03-22 14:19:37', '2017-03-22 14:19:37', '', 95, 'http://hospistuff.com/hrlfoundation/95-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
